1. Tartary buckwheat (TB) is associated with a decreased risk of type 2 diabetes mellitus (T2DM).
2. Type 2 diabetes mellitus (T2DM) can lead to the development of diabetic kidney disease (DKD).
3. Diabetic kidney disease (DKD) is a condition that can develop from type 2 diabetes mellitus (T2DM).
